Privacy Policy Opti Cleaner
Last updated: 29th November 2024
Introduction
Welcome to Opti Cleaner! This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you use our iOS application ("App") or when you contact us for support.
Information We Collect
When you use the Opti Cleaner App, we may collect certain information from you, including:
Device Information
: Information about your device, including your device type and operating system.
Usage Information
: Information such as the features you use and the actions you take within the App.
Subscription Information
: Information about your subscription, including the status and expiration date of your subscription.
Contact Information
: Your email address and any other information you provide when contacting our support team.
Location Information
: General location information based on your IP address to personalize and enhance your experience.
How We Use Your Information
We use the information collected to:
Provide and maintain the App's functionality.
Communicate with you, including sending updates, security alerts, and support messages.
Optimize and improve our services.
Provide you with customer support.
Comply with legal and regulatory requirements.
Sharing of Information
We may share your information with:
Third-party service providers that assist us in operating the App and providing our services.
Apple, in cases where we receive a refund request for an in-app purchase. We reserve the right to provide Apple with information regarding the user's in-app purchase consumption, including app usage time, anonymous account identifier, total amount spent, and total amount refunded.
Legal and regulatory authorities to comply with applicable laws, regulations, or legal requests.
Your Choices
Data Access and Control
: You can review and update certain personal information by accessing your account settings.
Opt-Out Options
: You can choose not to provide certain information, but this may limit your ability to use certain features of the App. You can also adjust your device settings to opt out of certain data collection.
Data Retention
We retain your information for as long as necessary to provide you with our services and as required to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.
Security
We take reasonable measures to protect information about you from loss, theft, misuse, and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.
International Data Transfers
Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than the country in which you are resident. These countries may have data protection laws that are different from the laws of your country.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at help@optidev.tech.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes to our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
Thank you for using Opti Cleaner!